Lines: Alright, it's time for the final battle.
DeepL_mtl: Okay, now it's time for the decisive battle.

Lines: Being at the forefront of the invasion...Finally!
DeepL_mtl: I can't believe I'm leading the charge....

Lines: There she goes again...
It's the most dangerous job there is, isn't it?
DeepL_mtl: It's the most dangerous job there is, right?

Lines: Although it seems that the enemy's defense forces
are concentrated around HQ and space port, which are
under attack by our main forces.
DeepL_mtl: But, well, the enemy's defensive forces seem to be concentrated in the main base facility and the section where the space facility is located, which is under attack by the main forces.

Lines: That's right.
This operation is race against time.
DeepL_mtl: This operation is a race against time anyway.

Lines: After arriving, please destroy targeted
facilities within time limit
DeepL_mtl: After entering the site, destroy the facilities targeted for attack within the time limit.

Lines: Once its done, Medea will perform combat landing to
unload ground troops, which will occupy enemy base.

Lines: Afterwards, all we have to do is protectet Medea, right?

Lines: Correct.
Battle will continue until we eliminate all enemies around,
or until main force overruns this base.
DeepL_mtl: The rest of the battle will continue until the main force that is attacking the base's main facility either overruns it or destroys the enemy in this section.

Lines: It's such a bit job!

We'll absolutely get home alive!
Well then, Unit 1! Let's go!

Absolutely all of us, and we'll get out of here alive.

Lines: Roger that!
